(2943, 409, 'homepageintrotext2', 'The use of precision tools in the demanding area of metal processing is today associated with ever higher requirements.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe face this challenge and manufacture tools with great quality awareness.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nOur cutting machine tools are now firmly positioned in the market and we use the satisfaction of and feedback from our customers in the redevelopment and further development of our products.\r\n\r\nAiming to be informative\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nOur company places great value on being a personal, competent point of reference for our customers. As such we can provide various contacts depending on your area of expertise.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIf your requests cannot be resolved immediately, we will continue to work on your requirements internally and will immediately inform you as soon as an outcome is available.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPersonal service matters to us.'),
