(384, 1, '2016-06-27 18:52:56', '2016-06-27 16:52:56', '<h1>With the expectation of perfection</h1>\nWelcome to our company.\n\nWe are an SME specialising in the sale of precision tools and machines for metal processing.\n\nOur company''s objective is to provide customers with the best solutions and products in this area. Furthermore we are a point of reference for complete solutions, and we support our customers with things such as the facilitation of capacities as well. As a result of our years of experience and the wide-ranging product and market knowledge of our management team and sales staff, we have succeeded in acquiring a large number of renowned customers despite the young age of the company, which was founded in January 2006.\n\nBesides our comprehensive technological knowledge, our customers are impressed with our successful collaborations with renowned industry manufacturers.', 'Company', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '149-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-06-27 18:52:56', '2016-06-27 16:52:56', '', 149, 'http://localhost/pzs_2/?p=384', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
